    <title>vsCode配置C环境</title>
    <url>/2022/03/29/vsCode%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEC%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="VsCode中配置-C-环境"><a href="#VsCode中配置-C-环境" class="headerlink" title="VsCode中配置 C 环境"></a>VsCode中配置 C 环境</h1><p>刚开始学习C 语言时，我们一般会使用 vc6 或者 dev C++ 两种工具。随着后来的学习，逐渐感觉这两种开发工具并没有非常的方便。在专业人员眼中，visual studio会更加系统，更加专业，但是我们学习使用的工具，推荐**<u>vscode</u>**。它非常的轻便，配置完成后，可以编译学习许多的语言，C、python、java、php等。</p>
<h3 id="1-开发环境"><a href="#1-开发环境" class="headerlink" title="1.开发环境"></a>1.开发环境</h3><p>操作系统：window10<br>vscode(官网下载):<a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/">https://code.visualstudio.com/</a><br>minGW-64:<a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw-w64/files/">https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw-w64/files/</a></p>
<h3 id="2-下载安装"><a href="#2-下载安装" class="headerlink" title="2.下载安装"></a>2.下载安装</h3><h4 id="2-1下载VsCode"><a href="#2-1下载VsCode" class="headerlink" title="2.1下载VsCode"></a>2.1下载VsCode</h4><p><img src="https://colson-max.github.io/2022/03/29/vsCode%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEC%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/1.png" alt="1"></p>
<p>进入官网，选择适合自己电脑的版本，下载后解压，具体步骤教程网上有许多，不一一阐述了。</p>
<h4 id="2-2下载MinGW-64"><a href="#2-2下载MinGW-64" class="headerlink" title="2.2下载MinGW-64"></a>2.2下载MinGW-64</h4><p>1.下载软件后解压缩，将文件夹mingw64放入C盘根目录下。<br>2.添加ming64里面的bin文件夹到系统环境变量(这一步不会有人不会吧)<br>3.打开cmd检验：(配置成功如图回显)<br>输入gcc<br><img src="https://colson-max.github.io/2022/03/29/vsCode%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEC%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/2.png" alt="2"><br>输入g++<br><img src="https://colson-max.github.io/2022/03/29/vsCode%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEC%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/3.png" alt="3"></p>
<h3 id="3-添加vscode插件"><a href="#3-添加vscode插件" class="headerlink" title="3.添加vscode插件"></a>3.添加vscode插件</h3><p>点击“扩展”，进行搜索</p>
<p><img src="https://colson-max.github.io/2022/03/29/vsCode%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEC%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/4.png" alt="4"></p>
<ol>
<li><p>Chinese (Simplified) Language Pack for Visual Studio Code插件。（中文插件）</p>
</li>
<li><p>**C/C++**插件</p>
</li>
<li><p>Code Runner插件，一键运行C/C++/Python/Java等语言程序的插件。<br><strong>注意</strong>：这里需要配置一下置扩展配置，把run in terminal勾选上。</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>C/C++ GNU Global</strong>插件。</p>
</li>
<li><p>**C/C++ Compile Run **插件。</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Prettier - Code formatter</strong> 插件，用于格式化文档和代码。</p>
</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="4-配置C语言开发环境"><a href="#4-配置C语言开发环境" class="headerlink" title="4.配置C语言开发环境"></a>4.配置C语言开发环境</h3><p>在自己设定的储存C文件的仓库路径下，新建两个个文件夹，路径中不能有中文出现。</p>
<p><img src="https://colson-max.github.io/2022/03/29/vsCode%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEC%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/5.png" alt="5.png"></p>
<p>在 .vscode 中创建以下配置文件</p>
<p><img src="https://colson-max.github.io/2022/03/29/vsCode%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEC%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/6.png" alt="6"></p>
<h4 id="4-1-配置文件内容："><a href="#4-1-配置文件内容：" class="headerlink" title="4.1 配置文件内容："></a>4.1 配置文件内容：</h4><p>c_cpp_propeities.json</p>
<figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;configurations&quot;</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;name&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;MinGW64&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;intelliSenseMode&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;gcc-x64&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;compilerPath&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;C:\\mingw64\\bin\\gcc.exe&quot;</span>,   <span class="comment">//注意路径要与自己电脑配置的路径一致</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;includePath&quot;</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;workspaceFolder&#125;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">            ],</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;cStandard&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;c11&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    ],</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;version&quot;</span>: <span class="number">4</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>launch.json</p>
<figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;version&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;0.2.0&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;configurations&quot;</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;name&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;C Launch (GDB)&quot;</span>, <span class="comment">// 配置名称，将会在启动配置的下拉菜单中显示</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;type&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;cppdbg&quot;</span>, <span class="comment">// 配置类型，这里只能为cppdbg</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;request&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;launch&quot;</span>, <span class="comment">// 请求配置类型，可以为launch（启动）或attach（附加）</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;targetArchitecture&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;x64&quot;</span>, <span class="comment">// 生成目标架构，一般为x86或x64</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;program&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;fileDirname&#125;/build/$&#123;fileBasenameNoExtension&#125;.exe&quot;</span>, <span class="comment">// 将要进行调试的程序的路径</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;args&quot;</span>: [], <span class="comment">// 程序调试时传递给程序的命令行参数，一般设为空即可</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;stopAtEntry&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">false</span>, <span class="comment">// 设为true时程序将暂停在程序入口处，一般设置为false</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;cwd&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;workspaceRoot&#125;&quot;</span>, <span class="comment">// 调试程序时的工作目录，一般为$&#123;workspaceRoot&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;externalConsole&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">true</span>, <span class="comment">// 调试时是否显示控制台窗口，一般设置为true显示控制台</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;internalConsoleOptions&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;neverOpen&quot;</span>, <span class="comment">// 如果不设为neverOpen，调试时会跳到“调试控制台”选项卡&quot;,</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;MIMode&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;gdb&quot;</span>, <span class="comment">// 指定连接的调试器</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;miDebuggerPath&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;C:\\mingw64\\bin\\gdb.exe&quot;</span>, <span class="comment">// 调试器路径</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">//请注意路径与自己电脑配置的一致性</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;setupCommands&quot;</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">                &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="attr">&quot;description&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;Enable pretty-printing for GDB&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="attr">&quot;text&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;-enable-pretty-printing&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="attr">&quot;ignoreFailures&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            ],</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;preLaunchTask&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;compile&quot;</span> </span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    ]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>tasks.json</p>
<figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;version&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;2.0.0&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;tasks&quot;</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;label&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;compile&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;command&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;gcc&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;args&quot;</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;file&#125;&quot;</span>, <span class="comment">// 指定编译源代码文件             </span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;-o&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;fileDirname&#125;/build/$&#123;fileBasenameNoExtension&#125;.exe&quot;</span>, <span class="comment">// 指定输出文件名</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;-O0&quot;</span>, <span class="comment">// 优化级别</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;-ggdb3&quot;</span>, <span class="comment">// 生成和调试有关的信息</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;-Wall&quot;</span>, <span class="comment">// 开启额外警告</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;-std=c11&quot;</span>, <span class="comment">// 使用c11标准</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;-Wno-format&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;-finput-charset=UTF-8&quot;</span>, <span class="comment">//输入编译器文本编码 默认为UTF-8</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;-fexec-charset=GB18030&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;-D _USE_MATH_DEFINES&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">            ],</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;type&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;shell&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            </span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;group&quot;</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="attr">&quot;kind&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;build&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="attr">&quot;isDefault&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125;,</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;presentation&quot;</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="attr">&quot;echo&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">true</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="attr">&quot;reveal&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;always&quot;</span>, <span class="comment">// 在“终端”中显示编译信息的策略，可以为always，silent，never</span></span><br><span class="line">                 <span class="attr">&quot;focus&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">false</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                 <span class="attr">&quot;panel&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;shared&quot;</span> <span class="comment">// 不同的文件的编译信息共享一个终端面板</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    ]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>之后就可以直接编写运行C程序了！！！</p>
<p>参考：</p>
<p><a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/30315894">https://www.zhihu.com/question/30315894</a></p>
<p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_27283619/article/details/103648264">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_27283619/article/details/103648264</a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/av18436497?p=2">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av18436497?p=2</a></p>
]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>-VsCode</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>hexo博客图片不显示解决方案</title>
    <url>/2022/04/02/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="hexo-博客图片无法显示解决方案"><a href="#hexo-博客图片无法显示解决方案" class="headerlink" title="hexo 博客图片无法显示解决方案"></a>hexo 博客图片无法显示解决方案</h1><h2 id="前言："><a href="#前言：" class="headerlink" title="前言："></a>前言：</h2><p>根据此问题，网上有许多的解决方法，我也试过很多，根本原因是 hexo 升级后，对应的插件 hexo-asset-image 并未升级，所遗留下来的 bug 。</p>
<h2 id="网上常见的解决方案"><a href="#网上常见的解决方案" class="headerlink" title="网上常见的解决方案"></a>网上常见的解决方案</h2><h3 id="1-修改博客配置"><a href="#1-修改博客配置" class="headerlink" title="1.修改博客配置"></a>1.修改博客配置</h3><p>修改博客根目录中 _config.yml 文件配置项 post_asset_folder 为 true:</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">post_asset_folder:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>之后当你通过” hexo new ‘文件名’ “ 新建博客后，会产生一个和文件同名的文件夹。</p>
<p><img src="https://colson-max.github.io/2022/04/02/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/1.png" alt="1"></p>
<h3 id="2-下载插件"><a href="#2-下载插件" class="headerlink" title="2.下载插件"></a>2.下载插件</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install https://github.com/CodeFalling/hexo-asset-image --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-md-格式语言插入图片"><a href="#3-md-格式语言插入图片" class="headerlink" title="3.md 格式语言插入图片"></a>3.md 格式语言插入图片</h3><p>自行 google/baidu</p>
<h2 id="修改BUG"><a href="#修改BUG" class="headerlink" title="修改BUG"></a>修改BUG</h2><p>开头也说到，这也可能是 hexo 自家的 bug 引起的。下面是修改方案：</p>
<p>修改 <code>node_module/hexo-asset-image/index.js</code> 中的（大概58行附近）</p>
<figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 原来的</span></span><br><span class="line">$(<span class="built_in">this</span>).attr(<span class="string">&#x27;src&#x27;</span>, config.root + link + src);   </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//修改为如下</span></span><br><span class="line">$(<span class="built_in">this</span>).attr(<span class="string">&#x27;src&#x27;</span>, data.permalink +src);		<span class="comment">//data.permalink 是全路径</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>





<p>参考：</p>
<p><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/ea78bdd0551f">https://www.jianshu.com/p/ea78bdd0551f</a></p>
<p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/androidV/article/details/105781570">https://blog.csdn.net/androidV/article/details/105781570</a></p>
]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>-Hexo</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>C语言基础</title>
    <url>/2022/04/02/C%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="C-语言基础"><a href="#C-语言基础" class="headerlink" title="C 语言基础"></a>C 语言基础</h1><h2 id="hello-world"><a href="#hello-world" class="headerlink" title="hello world"></a>hello world</h2><p>C程序：</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//helloWorld.c</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;hello world!\n&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>linux编译</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ gcc hello.c</span><br><span class="line">$ ./a.out</span><br><span class="line">hello world!</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>gcc命令依次执行四步操作：1.预处理    2.编译    3.汇编    4.链接</p>
<img src="https://colson-max.github.io/2022/04/02/C%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/04/02/C%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/1.png" class width="1">

<h2 id="1-数据类型"><a href="#1-数据类型" class="headerlink" title="1. 数据类型"></a>1. 数据类型</h2><h3 id="1-1-变量"><a href="#1-1-变量" class="headerlink" title="1.1 变量"></a>1.1 变量</h3><h4 id="1-1-1-概念"><a href="#1-1-1-概念" class="headerlink" title="1.1.1 概念"></a>1.1.1 概念</h4><p>变量相当于内存中一个数据存储空间的表示，通过变量名可以访问到变量(值)</p>
<h4 id="1-1-2-使用步骤"><a href="#1-1-2-使用步骤" class="headerlink" title="1.1.2 使用步骤"></a>1.1.2 使用步骤</h4><p>1.声明变量    int num;<br>2.赋值           num = 60;<br>3.使用命令    printf(“num = %d”,num);<br>—-或者 一步到位    int num = 60—-</p>
<h4 id="1-1-3-变量使用注意事项"><a href="#1-1-3-变量使用注意事项" class="headerlink" title="1.1.3 变量使用注意事项"></a>1.1.3 变量使用注意事项</h4><ol>
<li>变量表示内存中的一个存储区域（不同的数据类型，占用的空间大小不一样）</li>
<li>该区域有自己的名称 和类型</li>
<li>变量必须先声明，后使用</li>
<li>该区域的数据可以在同一类型范围内不断变化</li>
<li>变量在同一个作用域内不能重名</li>
<li>变量三要素 (变量名+值+数据类型)</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="1-2-常量"><a href="#1-2-常量" class="headerlink" title="1.2    常量"></a>1.2    常量</h3><h4 id="1-2-1-字面常量"><a href="#1-2-1-字面常量" class="headerlink" title="1.2.1 字面常量"></a>1.2.1 字面常量</h4><p>字面常量是直接写出的固定值，它包含C语言中可用的数据类型，可分为整型常量，字符常量等。</p>
<h4 id="1-2-2-const-修饰的常变量"><a href="#1-2-2-const-修饰的常变量" class="headerlink" title="1.2.2 const 修饰的常变量"></a>1.2.2 const 修饰的常变量</h4><p>C语言标准提供了 <strong>const</strong> 关键字，在定义变量的同时，在变量名之前加上 const 修饰。<br>值不能被修改，在整个作用域中都维持原值。</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> a = <span class="number">1</span>;	<span class="comment">//const修饰，a 是常变量，但 a 本质上依然是变量，具有&#x27;常&#x27;属性，不能被修改</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="1-2-3-define-定义的标识符常量"><a href="#1-2-3-define-定义的标识符常量" class="headerlink" title="1.2.3 define 定义的标识符常量"></a>1.2.3 define 定义的标识符常量</h4><p>C语言提供了 <strong>define</strong> 命令定义标识符常量，该标识符常量在程序中是个定值，通常用于代表数组容量或涉及数学的常量。</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">define</span> PI 3.14159</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">define</span> SIZE 10			<span class="comment">// SIZE 代表数组元素个数</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span>				<span class="comment">//如需修改数组大小，只需要将 SIZE 代表的值修改即可</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">int</span> arr[SIZE] = &#123;<span class="number">0</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="1-2-4-枚举常量"><a href="#1-2-4-枚举常量" class="headerlink" title="1.2.4 枚举常量"></a>1.2.4 枚举常量</h4><p>数值较小且为非负整数。如一周有7天等。C语言提供了一种<strong>枚举（Enum）类型</strong>，能够列出所有可能会用到的取值，并给它们取一个名字</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="class"><span class="keyword">enum</span> <span class="title">Sex</span>&#123;</span>				<span class="comment">//枚举常量     性别</span></span><br><span class="line">        MALE, </span><br><span class="line">        FEMALE,</span><br><span class="line">        SECRET</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="class"><span class="keyword">enum</span> <span class="title">Sex</span> <span class="title">s</span> =</span> FEMALE;  	<span class="comment">//利用枚举常量给变量赋值</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%d\n&quot;</span>, MALE);</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%d\n&quot;</span>, FEMALE);</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%d\n&quot;</span>,SECRET);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>注意：</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><p>不能对枚举常量赋值，只能将它们的值赋给其他的变量。</p>
</li>
<li><p>不能再定义与枚举常量名字相同的变量。</p>
</li>
<li><p>不能用<code>&amp;</code>取得它们的地址。</p>
</li>
</ul>
